Analysis.name: Adverse events (total): duration of administration subgroup analysis
Bias.arising.from.the.randomization.proc: Low risk

Computer-generated randomisation sequence. All study medications were identical in appearance and prepared by a study pharmacist that was likely independent of the enrollment personnel. Observed between-group differences in the distribution of baseline variables compatible with chance.

Footnotes: Data from first phase crossover provided by study author.
